in double quick time and get lots of
G. Then will go to lend to biggipon.

one million G from Momimi.

of gifts to a certain girlipon.

excited. Really likes girlipon!

rows.label: qst710702_msg0108

were big help of Momimi!

Pyrithium Trade Guild, too!
